= Future perspectives
With the SoC FPGA technology explained in great detail, a look towards the future of the technology is to be made.

What improvements can be expected from this technology? Well the advancements in technologies used in production and manufacturing process of SoC FPGAs are determined to improve, smaller chip production technology, integration of faster processor systems, and others.

The development of different new IPs is also a sign that this technology is still growing and expanding. With more companies jumping on the ship of SoC FPGA development, since the market is projected to grow, the future is looking bright for this technology.

